Marquis.

407
00:16:21,490 --> 00:16:22,470
We are just

408
00:16:22,490 --> 00:16:23,490
partners at work.

409
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:24,670
Don't listen to

410
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:26,300
the gossip of the commoners.

411
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:28,260
But I've heard that–

412
00:16:28,260 --> 00:16:28,840
Uncle.

413
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:30,130
You don't know.

414
00:16:30,510 --> 00:16:31,700
Miss Jiu'er is not

415
00:16:31,730 --> 00:16:32,390
like that.

