425
00:16:45,430 --> 00:16:47,010
How can you like this girl?

426
00:16:47,190 --> 00:16:48,780
I'd rather you like Han Zheng.

427
00:16:48,780 --> 00:16:49,340
Heyin.

428
00:16:49,830 --> 00:16:51,890
