429
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:54,800
He has always admired talented people.

430
00:16:55,590 --> 00:16:56,210
Alright.

431
00:16:56,690 --> 00:16:58,830
The story made me sad.

432
00:16:59,590 --> 00:17:02,700
