433
00:17:02,700 --> 00:17:03,560
Your Highness!

434
00:17:07,220 --> 00:17:08,020
Your Majesty.

435
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:09,420
Your Highness.

436
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:11,440
Something happened at the dock.

437
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,790
Something happened to the Starry Night.

438
00:17:12,790 --> 00:17:14,730
It seems to be related to the siren.

439
00:17:15,650 --> 00:17:16,420
The siren?

440
00:17:16,670 --> 00:17:17,800
The siren appeared?

441
00:17:18,220 --> 00:17:18,859
The siren?

442
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:35,520
This ship

443
00:17:35,810 --> 00:17:36,940
is really exactly the same

444
00:17:36,940 --> 00:17:38,140
as the one in my dream.

445
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:40,340
But I've never seen this ship

446
00:17:40,340 --> 00:17:41,270
before.

447
00:17:47,060 --> 00:17:48,260
Greetings, Your Highness.

448
00:17:48,260 --> 00:17:48,720
Lord Hu.

449
00:17:48,890 --> 00:17:49,600
How is it?

450
00:17:50,660 --> 00:17:51,520
Your Highness.

451
00:17:51,740 --> 00:17:53,360
Over 100 people on the Starry Night

452
00:17:53,360 --> 00:17:54,960
disappeared just like that.

453
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:56,770
There are no traces

454
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:57,840
of a fight.

455
00:17:58,750 --> 00:17:59,300
I’m afraid they have really

456
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:00,830
been captured by the siren.

457
00:18:01,290 --> 00:18:02,880
What is this siren

458
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,490
they're talking about?

459
00:18:05,420 --> 00:18:07,190
Over the past few years,

460
00:18:07,300 --> 00:18:08,160
once in a while,

461
00:18:08,330 --> 00:18:10,530
a ship will leave full and return empty.

462
00:18:11,170 --> 00:18:13,250
Sometimes, there were a few survivors.

463
00:18:13,250 --> 00:18:13,980
They said

464
00:18:14,330 --> 00:18:16,040
