465
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:17,530
No one could say

466
00:18:18,290 --> 00:18:19,700
what the siren looked like.

467
00:18:19,700 --> 00:18:20,910
The survivors all said

468
00:18:20,910 --> 00:18:22,590
their eyes had been closed,

469
00:18:22,610 --> 00:18:24,830
