470
00:18:24,830 --> 00:18:26,630
That's why the siren let them go.

471
00:18:26,650 --> 00:18:28,300
Anyone whose eyes had been open

472
00:18:28,300 --> 00:18:29,830
were captured by the siren.

473
00:18:34,540 --> 00:18:36,250
Is the siren extremely ugly?

474
00:18:36,570 --> 00:18:38,570
Is that why its afraid of being seen?

475
00:18:40,490 --> 00:18:41,940
Keep your voice down, Brother Han.

476
00:18:41,940 --> 00:18:43,260
Don't let the siren hear you.

477
00:18:43,260 --> 00:18:44,120
Why did you come

478
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,370
