496
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:50,820
Yes.

497
00:19:51,450 --> 00:19:52,770
So most of the missing people

498
00:19:52,770 --> 00:19:53,980
are Qi people.

499
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:55,900
Your Highness.

500
00:19:55,970 --> 00:19:57,170
Since the siren has reappeared,

501
00:19:57,170 --> 00:19:59,500
everyone in Jiuxiao City will be fearful.

502
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:01,780
Why don't we ask a shaman to conduct a ritual

503
00:20:01,780 --> 00:20:02,930
to pacify the people,

504
00:20:02,930 --> 00:20:04,300
