505
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:05,300
What do you think?

506
00:20:06,250 --> 00:20:07,380
Let's do as you said.

507
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:08,820
No.

508
00:20:10,130 --> 00:20:11,060
It's not a siren.

509
00:20:11,670 --> 00:20:12,730
It's not a siren?

510
00:20:14,610 --> 00:20:15,070
Jiu'er.

511
00:20:15,660 --> 00:20:16,920
Did you find anything?

512
00:20:17,620 --> 00:20:18,820
The Princess is here!

513
00:20:22,550 --> 00:20:24,080
Inspector Su, you're here.

514
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:25,700
Have you found any clues?

515
00:20:26,370 --> 00:20:26,830
Heyin.

516
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,770
