536
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:04,080
Listen up.

537
00:21:04,490 --> 00:21:05,970
Everyone is cheering you on.

538
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:08,150
They're counting on you to solve the case.

539
00:21:08,150 --> 00:21:08,950
Inspector Su.

540
00:21:09,370 --> 00:21:09,820
Yes.

541
00:21:10,190 --> 00:21:11,180
Yes, Inspector Su.

542
00:21:11,180 --> 00:21:11,620
Heyin.

