00:21:12,080 --> 00:21:13,100
Stop messing around.

544
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:13,700
Come here.

545
00:21:17,890 --> 00:21:18,690
Inspector Su.

546
00:21:18,910 --> 00:21:20,210
Inspector Su, I beg of you.

547
00:21:20,210 --> 00:21:21,030
Please help us.

548
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:22,360
Please catch the siren.

549
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:24,280
My husband was on the boat.

550
00:21:25,020 --> 00:21:26,150
He can only come back

551
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:27,600
