552
00:21:28,250 --> 00:21:29,700
Me too.

553
00:21:29,770 --> 00:21:31,170
My son was on the boat too.

554
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:32,690
Please!

555
00:21:32,890 --> 00:21:34,410
Please help us catch the siren.

556
00:21:34,410 --> 00:21:35,750
Get up first.

557
00:21:35,780 --> 00:21:36,290
Get up first.

558
00:21:36,290 --> 00:21:37,390
Please.

559
00:21:37,420 --> 00:21:37,880
Please.

560
00:21:38,390 --> 00:21:38,740
Okay.

561
00:21:39,460 --> 00:21:40,210
Don't worry.

562
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:41,360
The Inspection Bureau

563
00:21:41,360 --> 00:21:42,220
will do our best

564
00:21:42,350 --> 00:21:43,990
to help you find your loved ones.

565
00:21:43,990 --> 00:21:45,180
No matter what kind of monster it is,

566
00:21:45,180 --> 00:21:46,580
