567
00:21:47,890 --> 00:21:48,990
It's all Heyin's fault.

568
00:21:48,990 --> 00:21:50,040
Why did she have to make a fuss?

569
00:21:50,040 --> 00:21:50,610
Otherwise,

570
00:21:50,610 --> 00:21:51,150
you wouldn't have had to

571
00:21:51,150 --> 00:21:52,610
