575
00:21:58,490 --> 00:22:00,020
Even if Heyin wasn't there,

576
00:22:00,250 --> 00:22:02,710
I would still want to investigate this case.

577
00:22:03,610 --> 00:22:04,410
You're right.

578
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:06,760
Our Jiu'er has a strong sense of curiosity.

579
00:22:06,760 --> 00:22:07,630
Maybe you just wanted to see

580
00:22:07,630 --> 00:22:08,960
what the siren looks like, right?

581
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:10,130
My Jiu'er...

582
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:12,160
Do you really think

583
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,620
there's a siren?

584
00:22:13,890 --> 00:22:15,130
Qi people exist,

585
00:22:15,150 --> 00:22:16,320
so why can't a siren?

586
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:17,650
What do you mean?

587
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:19,630
You're saying we're monsters?

588
00:22:20,070 --> 00:22:21,650
Brother Han, you're being overzealous again.

